Class Application

java.lang.Object
BTO_Management_System.Application
public class Application extends Object
Represents an application submitted by an applicant for a specific BTO project. It tracks the applicant, the project applied for, the status of the application, the flat type requested, and the status of any withdrawal requests.

      applicationStatus - The initial status of the application.
